          "Collected and validated GNSS RTK positioning data and supported multi-UAV takeoff, trajectory tracking, and dynamic formation tests.",
        ],
      },
      {
        title: "GenreShift: Intelligent Genre Transformation with Quantitative Linguistics and LLMs",
        meta: "Project Lead · Oct 2024 - Nov 2025",
        bullets: [
          "Led quasi-parallel corpus construction, data crawling and cleaning, style feature extraction, LoRA fine-tuning, and Mixture-of-Experts system design.",
          "Coordinated the patent application for a genre transformation method and system based on quantitative linguistics and LLMs, application number 2025105553019.",
        ],
      },
    ],
    awards: [
      "National First Prize, China Robotics and Artificial Intelligence Competition, captain, 2025.",
      "National Champion, Intelligent Unmanned Systems Application Challenge, captain, 2025.",
      "National Second Prize, National Undergraduate Electronics Design Contest, captain, 2025.",
      "National Second Prize, RoboMaster University League, vision group lead, 2025.",
      "Honorable Mention, Mathematical Contest in Modeling, captain, 2024.",
    ],
    skills: [
      "Programming and robotics: ROS1/2, Python, C/C++, MATLAB, STM32, Arduino.",
      "Engineering tools: Fusion 360, SolidWorks, EDA design.",
      "Licenses: AOPA multirotor visual-line-of-sight pilot license, C1 driver's license.",
      "Languages: Chinese native, English TEM-4, French.",
      "Interests: badminton, football, cycling, FPV drones.",
    ],
  },
  zh: {
    name: "李溢涵",
    description: "李溢涵的学术简历，包括论文、实习经历、项目经历、奖项和技能。",
    contacts: [
      { label: "电话", value: "+86 18615276438", href: "tel:+8618615276438" },
      { label: "邮箱", value: "liyihan.xyz@gmail.com", href: "mailto:liyihan.xyz@gmail.com" },
      { label: "个人网站", value: "liyihan.xyz", href: "https://liyihan.xyz" },
      { label: "GitHub", value: "HY-LiYihan", href: "https://github.com/HY-LiYihan" },
      {
        label: "Google Scholar",
        value: "Profile",
        href: "https://scholar.google.com/citations?hl=en&user=Hmkl-ScAAAAJ",
      },
    ],
    sections: {
      publications: "学术成果",
      internships: "实习经历",
      projects: "项目经历",
      awards: "荣誉奖项",
      skills: "专业技能与其他",
    },
    publications: [
      {
        title: "OmniTrav: A Dataset and Benchmark for 360° Vision-based Traversability via Foundation Models",
        authors: "Yihan Li, Hao Ren, Zhenglan Jiang, Junzhe Zhu, Hui Cheng*",
        venue: "IROS 2026 submitted",
      },
      {
        title: "Unordered Landmark Visual Navigation",
        authors:
          "Hao Ren, Junzhe Zhu, Yihan Li, Zetong Bi, Le Zheng, Zhi Li, Yiqing Yuan, Zhaoliang Wan, Lu Qi, Hui Cheng",
        venue: "ECCV 2026 submitted",
      },
      {
        title:
          "RAPID Hand: A Robust, Affordable, Perception-Integrated, Dexterous Manipulation Platform for Generalist Robot Autonomy",
        authors:
          "Zhaoliang Wan, Zetong Bi, Zida Zhou, Hao Ren, Yiming Zeng, Yihan Li, Lu Qi, Xu Yang, Ming-Hsuan Yang, Hui Cheng",
        venue: "NeurIPS 2025",
      },
    ],
    internships: [
      {
        title: "Yun Drone",
        meta: "研发实习生 · 2025年6月 - 2026年3月",
        bullets: [
          "完成科研无人机硬件选型与系统集成，确定飞控、电调、传感器配置方案并优化载荷能力。",
          "执行飞行稳定性与机动性测试，基于飞行日志定位控制异常并提出 PID 调参建议。",
          "协同结构团队优化机体布局，确保敏感传感器的电磁兼容与减振性能。",
        ],
      },
    ],
    projects: [
      {
        title: "OmniTrav：面向 360° 视觉可通行性的数据集与基准",
        meta: "第一作者 · 合作导师：成慧 教授 · 2025年6月 - 2026年3月",
        bullets: [
          "提出 Camera-to-Traversability 流水线，将针孔、鱼眼、全景等相机 RGB 输入映射为 360° 径向通行距离向量。",
          "构建 OmniTrav 数据集，包含 4.7k 场景、25 万帧和 577 GB 数据，并设计基于基础模型的自动标注流水线。",
          "在多类相机上优于 ResNet-FC 与 DINOv3-MLP 基线，全景障碍检测 F1 达 1.0，针孔中位误差 0.27 m。",
        ],
      },
      {
        title: "RAPID Hand 感知融合灵巧手运动控制与抓取实验",
        meta: "科研助理 · 合作导师：成慧 教授 · 2024年11月 - 2025年6月",
        bullets: [
          "面向自研 20 自由度仿人灵巧手，开发实时底层运动控制驱动，建立稳定的 1 kHz 控制回路。",
          "完成腕部视觉、指尖触觉传感器与关节本体感知的同步与融合，将感知链路延迟稳定在 7 ms 以内。",
          "搭建高保真 MuJoCo 仿真环境开展 Sim2Real 验证，并基于 Diffusion Policy 训练全手视触觉策略。",
